  9  /-! # Stone-Čech compactification
 10  
 11  Construction of the Stone-Čech compactification using ultrafilters.
 12  
 13  Parts of the formalization are based on "Ultrafilters and Topology"
 14  by Marius Stekelenburg, particularly section 5.
 15  -/
 16  
 17  noncomputable theory
 18  
 19  open filter lattice set
 20  open_locale topological_space
 21  
 22  universes u v
 23  
 24  section ultrafilter
 25  /- The set of ultrafilters on α carries a natural topology which makes
 26    it the Stone-Čech compactification of α (viewed as a discrete space). -/
 27  
 28  /-- Basis for the topology on `ultrafilter α`. -/

195    build it as a quotient of `ultrafilter α` by the relation which

198    point of γ. -/
